page.title: 08Wild Flower Survey-Exbourne
page.content: The weather and climate are mild.The air is not polluted.Here is a list of wild flowers found in Exbourne.Red campion:wild parsley:foxgloves:Welsh poppies:honeysuckle:daisy:dandelion: dogrose:bluebell:greater celandine: ladies smock:wild garlic:charlock: shepherds purse:greater stitchwort: common mallow:wild sorrel:birdsfoot trefoil:red clover:meadowsweet:bramble strawberry:wall pennywort:hogweed:ivy: goosegrass:ladies bedstraw:woodruffe: oxeye daisy: groundsel:primrose: pimpernel:forgetmenot: deadly nightshade:germander speedwell: nettle:deadnettle:cuckoopint:early purple orchis:wild daffodil:snowdrop: tufted vetch:periwinkle. We did this survey in April and in July,to get a wider spectrum of plants.
